{"type":"answer","id":23994,"parentType":"question","parentId":4642,"uid":5864,"contents":"换个角度看问题，用符合赵家人语法的话语，诱导墙内民众思考，也不失为一种曲线救国的办法。看得懂的人就会知道是个笑话，看不懂的人就会被启发思考，直到看懂这个笑话。品葱的大神完全可以学习这种方法，“师赵长技以制赵”。用敌人的话语说服敌人，才是高招！这和<a href=\"http://www.mitbbs.com/article_t/Joke/34100019.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">社会主义小黄文</a>，<a href=\"https://welovexjp.github.io/post/pi-yao-xi-lie-yi-huan-yuan-suo-wei-liu-si-shi-jian-de-zhen-xiang/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扛着红旗反红旗</a>有异曲同工之妙。到时候遍地开花，才有得赵家人难受。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/06/03/5cf472651406760429.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/06/03/5cf472651406760429.png\" alt=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/06/03/5cf472651406760429.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n在《1984》的世界里，就算是用“新话”，也能传播我们想说的东西。","date":"2019-06-03","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}